{
  "title": "crossover-edtech-toolkit: An Open-Source Toolkit for Replicable Crossover Studies in Education",
  "description": "An open-source platform for replicable crossover (AB/BA) experimental studies in higher education, focused on evaluating the impact of generative AI on learning outcomes. Includes web-based data collection, validated instruments, R and Python analysis pipelines, a Monte Carlo simulation engine, and documentation.",
